| INV | V:TYPE | V:PROP | V:KANI | V:MODEL |
|-----|--------|--------|--------|---------|
| STORE-001 | monotonic type | proptest | kani::proof | stateright |
| STORE-002 | NonEmpty<T> | proptest | kani::proof | — |
